section Torus Creating the torus
state video on
state animation on
state cursor on

caption .5 .15 3 Click on the Create Torus icon to create a torus
moveover CreateTorusIcon 1
click
wait 2

caption .5 .15 3 Select the Translation Tool
moveover TranslationToolIcon 1
click
wait 2

caption .5 .15 3 Drag the right handle until the torus;\
    moves 5 units to the right
moveover TranslationTool/X/XSlider/MaxFace 1
drag .088 0 3
wait 2
